    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is slightly softened, reduce the heat to low</p><p>Add the<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> ground paprika </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), stir it all together and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
