      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>long grain white rice</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving – this is your <strong>tomato spiced rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1691057306003-x200.jpg",
