            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, cut a large piece of<strong> tin foil</strong> approx. the size of A3 sheet of paper</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Make 2 separate parcels!</p><p>Add the<strong> basa fillets</strong> to the middle of the foil</p><p>Pour the <strong>peanut sauce </strong>evenly over the <strong>basa fillets</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1691057309829-x200.jpg",
