            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-1691057317269-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>West African-style peanut basa</strong> with the <strong>spiced tomato rice</strong> and <strong>cooked green beans </strong>to the side</p><p>Spoon the <strong>remaining peanut sauce</strong> from the parcel over the basa and sprinkle with the <strong>crispy fried onions</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
